<p>
  <span class="nym">Paul</span>
  <span class="gen">m.</span>
  
  <span class="etym"><span class="lang">Latin</span> <i>paulus</i> 'small, little'.
  </span>
  
</p>
  
<div class="usg">
  <p>The name of a biblical saint and apostle, as well as  a number of early Roman and Egyptian saints, one of the founding saints of Brittany, and a 13th C Dominican saint and martyr.  Greek New Testament: <i>Παῦλος</i>. Vulgate: <i>Paulus</i>. Wycliffite Bible (1395): <i>Paul</i>.</p>
</div>
  
  


